{"tid":2364753,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果新專利：內置 AirPods 收納及充電的iphone保護殼","createTime":"2021-01-13T08:24:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T04:21:43.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"77f4238af00f467501d4a079a4e406642f14416c","tid":2364753,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T08:24:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PM4kAJ9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPM4kAJ9.jpg&h=4c883fc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從 iPhone 4 的 Bumper 到 iPhone 12 的 MagSafe 系列，蘋果官方推出的保護殼逐漸衍生出更多功能性。而從蘋果最新的專利文件來看，未來的的官方殼或許還能玩出更多花樣。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國專利商標局披露的最新專利文件，蘋果提交了一項關於內置配件充電模塊的保護殼的專利申請，圖中顯示這款保護殼內置了收納 AirPods 或其他耳機的充電模塊，蘋果設計了不同樣式的耳機收納模塊，有些位於保護殼內側，有些位於保護殼頂部，但相似點都是能夠利用手機的電量為耳機緊急補電。"},{"pid":"db6bb9c9ed69944a6817c8e611dbe7862730f063","tid":2364753,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T08:25:39.000Z","msg":"蘋果經常提交大量專利作為技術積累，其中很大一部分都只是存在理論可行性，不一定會投入使用。但管中窺豹，通過這些專利技術或許能夠猜測蘋果的研究動態，幫助我們瞭解蘋果正在研究的一些領域和未來可能發力的方向。"},{"pid":"0ff82c80e49daf0ac0828b9947087f6fd701e6e2","tid":2364753,"uid":187676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T10:21:45.000Z","msg":"出個official magsafe 尿袋先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1af66b3e1f894693c77cb70afbd06836acc5d5dd","tid":2364753,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T11:02:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1adc1af790f8aac2025df962cb09917b52d30053","tid":2364753,"uid":96708,"like":3,"dislike":12,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T11:25:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/3b/c8/a0/3bc8a079172a2d12739309a55f4d5e2a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F3b%2Fc8%2Fa0%2F3bc8a079172a2d12739309a55f4d5e2a.png&h=db685846&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"155